v1|craft-orchestration-index
=ROUTING
in-progress story|AskUser: Continue? ‚Üí story-continue
planning cycle|All ready? ‚Üí cycle-start | Still planning? ‚Üí cycle-design
pending requests|AskUser: Review? ‚Üí /craft Step 5b
status:planning (no chunks)|plan-chunks first
status:ready|story-implement
in backlog|cycle-assign first
mid-chunk (CHUNK>0)|Continue implement loop
validation FAILED (test)|test-fix (via story-implement)
validation FAILED (build/lint)|refine-chunk (via story-implement)
all stories complete|cycle-complete
post-cycle|analyze (QA,UX,Creative,Style)
known bug/post-story issue (no active story)|craft:fix (adhoc,no story needed)
deferral marker in user utterance ("later"/"don't let me forget"/"side note"/etc.)|inline-mention /craft:notebook (NOT AskUserQuestion); on accept invoke silently with session-context body+tags
lifecycle verb + named/deictic ref|graduate=inline-offer with named referent / done=AUQ confirmation always (even at HIGH conf - asymmetric failure visibility); LOW=no action
riff signal (user has room)|tacit-boundary "show me cases"=TIGHT flip-loop in main-loop (Read reference/calibration-loop.md) | blank-canvas "let's wander"=WIDE‚Üícraft:riff agent (Agent tool) | soft creative tradeoff=PRESIGNAL ignorable inline offer (NOT AUQ) | mid-task future spark=FOCUS GATE‚Üínotebook | micro choice=FLOOR silent. ‚â§1 inline offer/turn (no stacking w/ notebook/creative-spark/design-vibe)
=LOOP
Per chunk 1..N:
1.create-checkpoint.sh [story] [chunk]
2.INVOKE implementer via Task (NEVER implement directly)
3.INVOKE chunk-validator via Task (haiku)
4.PASSED:complete-chunk.sh‚Üínext chunk | FAILED:Read validate-fix-loop.md‚Üífix(Skill)‚Üíre-validate
5.Loop to 1
After all: chunk-validator final‚Üíclaims-audit‚Üíself-critique‚Üícomplete-story.sh
=CHAINS
story-implement‚Üí[checkpoint‚Üíimplementer(Task)‚Üíchunk-validator(haiku)‚Üípass:complete-chunk.sh‚Üífail:Read validate-fix-loop.md‚Üífix(Skill)‚Üíre-validate]√óN‚Üíchunk-validator final‚Üíclaims-audit‚Üícomplete-story.sh
test-fix‚Üítriage‚ÜíHAND BACK TO story-implement
refine-chunk‚Üísurgical fix‚ÜíHAND BACK TO story-implement
cycle-design‚Üícontent-spark(per story)‚Üícreative-spark(opt)‚Üídesign-vibe‚Üíplan-chunks MODE=batch
story-new‚Üícontent-spark‚Üícreative-spark(opt)‚Üíplan-chunks
fix‚Üíinvestigate‚Üíconfidence-check‚ÜíON yes:edit‚Üívalidate symptom|ON no:escalate‚Üístory-new
notebook‚Üícapture | notebook‚Üícapture‚Üídone (conversational, AUQ always) | notebook‚Üícapture‚Üígraduate(conversational)‚Üístory-new (pre-fills spark, flags source on success)
=RULES
!implement chunks directly‚ÄîALWAYS invoke implementer via Task
!validate directly‚Äîinvoke chunk-validator via Task (validate-chunk skill is manual-only)
!edit .state/.global-state directly‚Äîuse transition scripts
!run_in_background for test/typecheck/lint/build‚Äîmust be synchronous
!override FAILED verdict‚ÄîFAILED means FAILED
!present story content from memory‚ÄîRead file fresh
!batch concerns‚Äîsurface each via AskUserQuestion
+checkpoint before each chunk (create-checkpoint.sh)
+transition scripts for state changes
+breadcrumb before nested skill invocation
+clean up breadcrumb on ALL exit paths
!stop after chunk/story completes‚Äîcontinue to next chunk or next story
!conflate notebook todos with TaskCreate‚Äîdifferent lifetimes (notebook=persistent across sessions, TaskCreate=ephemeral, /craft:fix=adhoc-bug)
=SCRIPTS
start-cycle.sh [cycle]|activate,set ACTIVE_CYCLE
complete-cycle.sh|archive,clear ACTIVE_CYCLE
start-story.sh [file]|set CURRENT_STORY,CHUNK=1,status=active
complete-story.sh [file]|clear CURRENT_STORY,status=complete
complete-chunk.sh|increment CURRENT_CHUNK
create-checkpoint.sh [story] [chunk]|git commit+snapshot
update-global-state.sh KEY VAL|safe .global-state update
=STATE
.craft/.global-state|ACTIVE_CYCLE,CURRENT_STORY,PLANNING_CYCLE,RUN_MODE
.craft/cycles/{c}/.state|CURRENT_CHUNK,TOTAL_CHUNKS,CURRENT_STORY
.craft/cycles/{c}/cycle.yaml|title,goal,status(planning|ready|active|complete)
Story frontmatter:status|planning‚Üíready‚Üíactive‚Üícomplete
.craft/.continuation|breadcrumb for nested skills(30min TTL,one-shot)
.craft/settings.yaml|default_mode,parallel planning
.craft/design/locked.md|locked decisions(enforced by validation)
.craft/design/tokens.yaml|design tokens(enforced by style-analyzer)
.craft/fixes/*.md|adhoc fix records(category,root cause,validation)
.craft/.active-fix|safety marker for in-progress fix(session-start clears)
